snippet.title: Lando - Me? A Hero?(Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
#steam #videogames #landomeahero
Transported by an angel, fight and evolve in this rogue like! Combine powers, conquer worlds, and face relentless foes. Will you be the hero?

Play Now On Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3252090/Lando_Me_A_Hero/ 
Official Soundtrack: https://distrokid.com/hyperfollow/littlehope/lando-me-a-hero-official-soundtrack

Videogame by: Dario Criscuolo
